text: Yamandú Ramón Antonio Orsi Martínez (born 13 June 1967) is a Uruguayan politician who has been the 43rd and current president of Uruguay since 2025. He won the 2024 general election. He is a member of the left-wing Broad Front Party. He was the 22nd and 24th intendant of the Canelones Department from 2015 to February 2020, and from November 2020 to 2024. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Uruguay Category:Current national leaders
